# BackLog
### User Stories
1. As a new player I want to create a new account so I can play with my own unique username.  :)
2. As a returning player I want to loggin so I can play. :)
3. As a player I want to adjust the screen size to my liking.
4. As a player I want to adjust the different sounds to my liking.
5. As a player I want to create a character with a unique name I create.
6. As a player I want to have a variety of different background colors so I can pick one that lets me play the most comfortably.
7. As a player I would like to save my game and come back when I'm free again.
8. As a player I would like to replay the same scenario I just died in to see if I can fix my mistakes.
9. As a player I would like to type my commands into the text box and submit it with "ENTER". 
10. As a player I would like to click on the directions I want to go so I don't have to type it everytime.
11. As a player I would like to click the red search button to search the room so I don't have to type it.
12. As a player I would like to use the arrow keys to navigate the map so I have less to type.
13. As a player I would like to see what room im currently in in relation to the world I have explored.
14. As a player I would like to see what current actions I have available to me so I can strategically decide what to do next.
15. As a player I would like to view my current inventory so I know what I have and what I might need.
16. As a player I want to break down a door so I don't have to go looking for a key that might not exist.
17. As a player I want to see my previous actions and events so I know if I made a wrong move.
18. As a player I want to be able to drop inventory items so I can make room for better stuff.
19. As a player I want to read the description of the area I'm currently in so I know what might be there.
20. As a player I want to see when an event is triggered so I know I have to act quickly to survive.
21. As a player I want to load my last saved game so I can continue.
22. As a player I want to see how many times I died and survived so i can compare my performance to my friends.
23. As a player I want to take items I find after searching an area so I can have a better chance at survival.
24. As a player I would like to monitor my health so I now when to use a medkit.
25. As a player I would like to see what level I am currently and how long till my next level up so I know when I can use a weapon that Is too high a level for me .
26. As a player I want to increase different attributes so I can customize my character to my play style.
27. As a player I would like to use items in my inventory that are consumable so I can boost my stats or recover my lost hit points.
28. As a player I would like to equip different armor I find around the world so I can improve my survivability.
29. As a player I would like to attack so I can kill before I get killed.
30. As a player I would like to defend so I can reduce the amount of damage done to me.
31. and continue where I left off
